---
const projects = [
  {
    title: 'Home Service Estimate Engine',
    type: 'Focused Offer + Demo System',
    stack: 'Astro, Widget Frontend, API-backed estimate flow',
    image: '/assets/images/home-service-demo.png',
    alt: 'Home service estimate demo showing the guided lead capture flow',
    highlights: ['Guided estimate flow', 'Qualified lead capture', 'Reusable offer architecture'],
    problem:
      'Home service businesses often rely on generic contact forms that create weak quote requests, repetitive intake work, and poor lead context for the office team.',
    approach:
      'I treated the estimator as both a productized service offer and a working software proof. The public page explains the business value, while the live demo proves the estimator flow can be delivered as a real client-facing system.',
    solution:
      'Built a focused estimator offer page tied to a live demo that shows guided intake, estimate logic, and structured lead capture for home service companies.',
    outcome:
      'The project now works as both portfolio proof and a niche sales asset. It gives prospects a clearer picture of what they could buy, not just what I can code.',
    referenceLabel: 'Offer page',
    referenceHref: '/home-service-estimator',
    referenceText: 'View the estimator offer',
    referenceExternal: false,
    fallbackTitle: 'Focused offer',
    fallbackBody: 'Live page and demo available',
    tags: ['Astro', 'Lead generation', 'Productized service'],
  },
  {
    title: 'Travel Agency Website',
    type: 'Operational Website',
    stack: 'HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript',
    image: '/assets/images/travel-agency.png',
    alt: 'Travel agency website showing service sections and contact flow',
    highlights: ['Lead-focused structure', 'Mobile-first delivery', 'Low-maintenance stack'],
    problem:
      'The agency needed a stronger digital presence and a clearer inquiry path. Prospective customers were not getting enough structure, trust signals, or fast contact options from the previous setup.',
    approach:
      'I treated the site as an operational sales asset rather than a simple brochure. The build focused on mobile clarity, fast loading, direct contact paths, and a structure the client could maintain without overhead.',
    solution:
      'Delivered a static business website with clear service sections, trust-building content, responsive layouts, and contact flows designed to turn interest into real inquiries.',
    outcome:
      'The business gained a more credible online presence and a smoother path from first visit to direct inquiry, especially for mobile users comparing providers and reaching out quickly.',
    referenceLabel: 'Live reference',
    referenceHref: 'https://blessedjourneyglobal.com',
    referenceText: 'blessedjourneyglobal.com',
    fallbackTitle: 'Project preview',
    fallbackBody: 'Live example available',
    tags: ['Responsive design', 'Mobile-first', 'Performance-conscious'],
  },
  {
    title: 'Church Management System',
    type: 'Custom Business System',
    stack: 'Django REST Framework, Next.js, TypeScript',
    image: '/assets/images/religious-org.png',
    alt: 'Church management platform interface with structured navigation',
    highlights: ['Role-based access', 'Centralized records', 'Operational reporting'],
    problem:
      'The organization was handling members, events, attendance, and announcements through disconnected manual processes. That created duplicated work, inconsistent records, and avoidable administrative overhead.',
    approach:
      'I designed the system around a clear API-first architecture so business rules stayed centralized and the interface stayed focused on usability. That made the platform easier to secure, maintain, and extend.',
    solution:
      'Built a full-stack management platform covering member records, event scheduling, attendance tracking, announcements, and secure role-based access for staff and leadership.',
    outcome:
      'Administrative workload dropped by roughly 60 percent, and the organization moved from scattered records to a single operational system that supports day-to-day coordination.',
    referenceLabel: 'Reference',
    referenceText: 'Private and confidential',
    fallbackTitle: 'Internal platform',
    fallbackBody: 'Preview withheld for client privacy',
    tags: ['Python', 'Next.js', 'REST API'],
  },
];
---

<section class="projects section-padding" id="projects">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Selected Work</h2>
      <p>Examples of business-facing systems, internal platforms, and focused offers built to solve operational problems clearly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="projects-grid">
      {projects.map((project) => (
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="project-image-wrapper">
            <div class:list={['project-media', { 'is-fallback': !project.image }]}>
              {project.image && (
                <img
                  src={project.image}
                  alt={project.alt}
                  width="600"
                  height="400"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="project-image"
                  onerror="this.closest('.project-media').classList.add('is-fallback');"
                />
              )}
              <div class="project-fallback" aria-hidden="true">
                <span>{project.fallbackTitle}</span>
                <strong>{project.fallbackBody}</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-content">
            <div class="project-meta" aria-label="Project type and technologies">{project.type} | {project.stack}</div>
            <h3>{project.title}</h3>

            <div class="project-highlights" role="list">
              {project.highlights.map((highlight) => (
                <span class="project-highlight" role="listitem">{highlight}</span>
              ))}
            </div>

            <div class="project-section">
              <h4>Problem</h4>
              <p class="project-description">{project.problem}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="project-section">
              <h4>Approach</h4>
              <p>{project.approach}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="project-section">
              <h4>Solution</h4>
              <p class="project-description">{project.solution}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="project-tech" role="list">
              {project.tags.map((tag) => (
                <span class="tech-tag" role="listitem">{tag}</span>
              ))}
            </div>

            <div class="project-section">
              <h4>Outcome</h4>
              <p class="project-result">{project.outcome}</p>
            </div>

            <p class="project-reference">
              <strong>{project.referenceLabel}:</strong>{' '}
              {project.referenceHref ? (
                <a
                  href={project.referenceHref}
                  target={project.referenceExternal === false ? undefined : '_blank'}
                  rel={project.referenceExternal === false ? undefined : 'noopener nofollow'}
                >
                  {project.referenceText}
                </a>
              ) : (
                <span>{project.referenceText}</span>
              )}
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .projects {
    background-color: var(--color-light);
  }

  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .project-card {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .project-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .project-card:focus-within {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    outline-offset: 4px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  .project-image-wrapper {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius) 0 0;
  }

  .project-media {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(38, 70, 83, 0.95), rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.7));
  }

  .project-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .project-media.is-fallback .project-image {
    display: none;
  }

  .project-card:hover .project-image {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .project-fallback {
    display: none;
    min-height: 240px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .project-media.is-fallback .project-fallback {
    display: flex;
  }

  .project-fallback span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .project-fallback strong {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .project-content {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .project-meta,
  .project-card h3,
  .project-card p {
    margin-left: 0;
    margin-right: 0;
  }

  .project-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .project-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .project-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .project-highlight {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background-color: rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.08);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .project-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .project-section h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .project-description {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .project-tech {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .tech-tag {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background-color: var(--color-light);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .project-result {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .project-reference {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .project-reference a {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
